## What is Swagger

Swagger is an **automatic API documentation and testing tool**. It reads your controller code and builds a visual webpage where you can see all APIs and test them directly in the browser.

```
http://localhost:8081/swagger-ui.html  → Item Service APIs
http://localhost:8082/swagger-ui.html  → Inventory Service APIs
http://localhost:8083/swagger-ui.html  → Notification Service APIs
http://localhost:8084/swagger-ui.html  → Audit Service APIs
```

On each page you can:
- See all available endpoints
- See what JSON format is expected
- Click Try it out and test the API
- See the actual response

